  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">
      Output: "🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL — `.cs` modification + binding Q1 resolution logic + downstream blocker for task 005". Read project CLAUDE.md + spec.md FR-03/FR-04.
    </step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">
      Verify 001 ✅. Update `current-task.md` to task 003.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources">
      Read inputs + knowledge files. Capture baseline publish size for delta calc.
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="Inspect Existing Resolver">
      Open `IScopeResolverService` + implementation. Identify the canonical method shape for inheritance-chain resolution. Note: parent-walk logic, tenant filter, query batching.
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Add Resolution Methods">
      Extend interface with `GetPersonasAsync(tenantId, paging)` and `ResolvePersonaForChatAsync(tenantId, playbookId?) → AnalysisPersona`. Implement most-specific-wins: query playbook-attached first; fall through to tenant CUST-; fall through to global SYS-. Cache resolution with `tenantId`-keyed cache key per ADR-014 if caching is applied.
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Add Unit Tests">
      Comprehensive unit tests in `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/`: (a) no overrides → SYS- default; (b) tenant override → CUST- wins; (c) playbook override → playbook-attached wins; (d) playbook missing parent → falls through; (e) tenant isolation (different tenant cannot see another tenant's CUST-); (f) cache key includes tenantId.
    </step>
    <step order="6" name="Build + Verify Publish Size">
      `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` → 0 errors. `dotnet publish -c Release` → measure delta vs baseline; report ≤+5 MB R6 budget.
    </step>
    <step order="7" name="Verify Acceptance Criteria">
      Walk each criterion below; record evidence.
    </step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL rigor)">
      Run `code-review` + `adr-check` against changed `.cs` files. Verify ADR-010 / ADR-013 / ADR-014 / NFR-01 / NFR-14 compliance. Both gates MUST pass.
    </step>
    <step order="10" name="Document + Complete">
      Update task POML status complete. TASK-INDEX 003 ✅. Reset `current-task.md`. Report.
    </step>
  </steps>

